<plot>The young film-student and director Björn Last is trying to figure out why he wasn't able to complete his documentary about his hometown Braunschweig. He searches for enlightenment through a project colloquy with his film professor Gerd Roscher and the idea to make a short film about the unfinished work. He also conducts an interview about the troubled project and dreams about his next feature, which reflects the difficulties of an intimate, yet artistic process.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?044646</url></doc>
